title: Geert Wilders' visa delay 'an assault on freedom of speech', says new anti-Islam party Australian ...
text: The president of a new anti-Islam party due to be launched by Geert Wilders in Perth later this month accuses Australian authorities of "stonewalling" the controversial Dutch MP's visa. ...
